{
  "title": "DebugLayer",
  "description": "Abstract base for a single diagnostic overlay layer. Subclasses produce a visual (outlines, text panels, sparklines, etc.) that DebugOverlay composites each frame when visible is `true`. Concrete layers are tree-shakeable via the `@codexo/exojs/debug` subpath and are not loaded unless explicitly imported.",
